SubjectTwo-Lane International Bridge South of the Baudette-Rainy River International Bridge ** Construction **
PrecisOrder Approving the construction and operation of a new two-lane replacement Baudette-Rainy River International Bridge and the alteration by demolition of the existing bridge, pursuant to the INTERNATIONAL BRIDGES AND TUNNELS ACT, subject to terms and conditions established to mitigate safety and security risks.
